Class WorkTicketDAO

java.lang.Object
  db.WorkTicketDAO

public class WorkTicketDAO
extends java.lang.Object

Handles database access for the work ticket system. Displays the work ticket items and collects user input to create work tickets. This is a Data Access Object (DAO).
